        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Energy Emergency Leadership Act</b></p> <p>This bill requires the Secretary of Energy to assign energy emergency and energy security functions to an Assistant Secretary, including responsibilities with respect to infrastructure and cybersecurity.</p> <p>The Department of Energy must ensure that such functions are performed in coordination with relevant federal agencies.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
